                  SALOMONS ETHICKES. THE ſecond BOOKE. PRVDENCE.
                  
                     §. 1. Of Vertue in cōmon:

                           Wherein it conſiſteth.
                           Whereby it is ruled, and directed.
                        
                     
                     
                        
